    <p>“…or in the same projection for analyses on a regional scale to provide...” </p>
    <p>Thank you. We changed it to: “…or in the same equal area projection for analyses on a smaller scale to provide...” </p>
    <p>Line 239: suggest deleting “animal and plant” </p>
