    <p>Line 302-307: suggest turning this whole paragraph into one or two sentences at the end of previous paragraph </p>
    <p>Thank you. However, we think it would be better to break this down into two paragraphs as it will make it more clear to the reader that the tool has no limitations and that sources are available for ecosystems other than just terrestrial.</p>
    <p>Line 328: suggest deleting “still” </p>
